Author: hollisbecky
Text: Yep, coworker just started Keto this week and I was like “watch I can lose more than you”! Why??? This is just crazy.

Author: stegasaurus-
Text: if it helps, i do this every time any person mentions to me that they’re trying to lose weight, something in me cannot just let it slide and it HAS to become a competition. it’s the worst, but i feel you 😕
